250
00:22:37,160 --> 00:22:40,319
[SPEAKER_01] Neko ko je tu, ko je stvarno tu.

251
00:22:40,319 --> 00:22:42,599
[SPEAKER_01] I to što si tu,

252
00:22:42,599 --> 00:22:47,279
