298
00:24:27,720 --> 00:24:29,059
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, što konkretno?

299
00:24:29,059 --> 00:24:30,619
[SPEAKER_01] Odnos, kontakt.

300
00:24:30,619 --> 00:24:37,559
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

301
00:24:37,559 --> 00:24:40,599
[SPEAKER_01] opet ću se vratiti možda na neki primjer.

302
00:24:42,259 --> 00:24:43,599
[SPEAKER_01] Možeš se povezati

303
00:24:43,599 --> 00:24:45,819
[SPEAKER_01] da s nekim ljudima u životu

304
00:24:45,819 --> 00:24:47,220
[SPEAKER_01] vrlo često su to

305
00:24:47,220 --> 00:24:49,900
[SPEAKER_01] ili dobri prijatelji

306
00:24:49,900 --> 00:24:51,440
[SPEAKER_01] ili emocionalni partneri.

307
00:24:51,440 --> 00:24:53,420
