2688
01:34:20,659 --> 01:34:22,720
[SPEAKER_01] I da ti onda pričam o sebi.

2689
01:34:22,720 --> 01:34:24,680
[SPEAKER_01] I pričam ti o sebi,

2690
01:34:24,680 --> 01:34:27,180
[SPEAKER_01] a ti me ubereš i daš mi mirroring.

2691
01:34:27,180 --> 01:34:29,180
[SPEAKER_01] I taj proces se treba,

2692
01:34:29,180 --> 01:34:31,020
[SPEAKER_01] se događa u ranom periodu.

2693
01:34:31,020 --> 01:34:34,159
[SPEAKER_01] Imamo djete koje dođe kući

2694
01:34:34,159 --> 01:34:35,720
[SPEAKER_01] i kaže, mama, desilo mi se to,

2695
01:34:35,720 --> 01:34:37,220
[SPEAKER_01] djeca su me vamo tamo.

2696
01:34:37,220 --> 01:34:40,880
[SPEAKER_01] I to je trenutak gdje mama umjesto da kaže,

2697
01:34:40,880 --> 01:34:42,640
[SPEAKER_01] te šta si ovo, zašto si ono,

2698
01:34:42,640 --> 01:34:43,760
[SPEAKER_01] trebao si ovo, ono,

2699
01:34:43,760 --> 01:34:45,640
[SPEAKER_01] ili dođi, ajde, jadno djeto,

2700
01:34:45,640 --> 01:34:48,300
[SPEAKER_01] da kaže ono, ovo zlato,

2701
01:34:48,340 --> 01:34:50,119
[SPEAKER_01] vidim da ti je, ne znam,

2702
01:34:50,119 --> 01:34:53,500
[SPEAKER_01] teško ili vidim da osjetim da si

2703
01:34:53,500 --> 01:34:55,960
[SPEAKER_01] jako povređen s tim što su ti.

2704
01:34:55,960 --> 01:34:57,239
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, da te uberem

2705
01:34:57,239 --> 01:34:58,760
[SPEAKER_01] i da ti dam feedback

2706
01:34:58,760 --> 01:35:00,819
[SPEAKER_01] o onome čemu pričaš.

2707
01:35:01,500 --> 01:35:03,460
[SPEAKER_01] I to taj trenutak kad se desi,

2708
01:35:03,460 --> 01:35:05,260
[SPEAKER_01] recimo u terapiji, kad se to desi,

2709
01:35:05,260 --> 01:35:07,539
[SPEAKER_01] ljudi znaju se rasplakati jer ono,

2710
01:35:07,539 --> 01:35:09,380
[SPEAKER_01] konačno me neko razumije,

2711
01:35:09,380 --> 01:35:10,840
[SPEAKER_01] konačno me neko skužio.

2712
01:35:10,840 --> 01:35:13,760
[SPEAKER_01] A to je to što djetetu treba u ranom periodu.

2713
01:35:13,840 --> 01:35:15,939
[SPEAKER_01] kako djete ima puno takvih iskustava,

2714
01:35:15,939 --> 01:35:19,220
[SPEAKER_01] izrasta u osobu koja zna ko je,

2715
01:35:19,220 --> 01:35:21,359
[SPEAKER_01] koja ima slobodu da se izrazi

2716
01:35:21,359 --> 01:35:23,140
[SPEAKER_01] i sad, idemo na onaj pojam,

2717
01:35:23,140 --> 01:35:25,319
[SPEAKER_01] od prije, mogu biti autentičan.

2718
01:35:25,319 --> 01:35:27,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sad znam kako biti autentičan.

2719
01:35:29,100 --> 01:35:30,880
[SPEAKER_01] Jer često ljudi kažu na terapiji

2720
01:35:30,880 --> 01:35:32,979
[SPEAKER_01] svi govori o tome biti autentičan.

2721
01:35:32,979 --> 01:35:35,899
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ne znam kako je biti autentičan.

2722
01:35:35,899 --> 01:35:38,340
[SPEAKER_01] Ja znam kakav bi ja trebao biti

2723
01:35:38,340 --> 01:35:40,039
[SPEAKER_01] u smislu šta se tad radi,

2724
01:35:40,039 --> 01:35:41,579
[SPEAKER_01] kako se tad ponaša ovo ono,

2725
01:35:41,579 --> 01:35:43,159
[SPEAKER_01] ali to ne ide iz mene.

2726
01:35:43,159 --> 01:35:45,500
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ja ne znam šta ja ni hoću,

2727
01:35:45,500 --> 01:35:46,359
[SPEAKER_01] ni osjećam,

2728
01:35:46,359 --> 01:35:48,579
[SPEAKER_01] ja se ne mogu povezati sa sobom.

2729
01:35:48,579 --> 01:35:51,819
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ovoga nije bilo.

2730
01:35:51,819 --> 01:35:56,739
[SPEAKER_00] Često komentiram sa gustima

2731
01:35:56,739 --> 01:35:59,920
[SPEAKER_00] taj koncept autentičnosti.

2732
01:35:59,920 --> 01:36:03,600
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ga sebi dan-danas nisam

2733
01:36:03,600 --> 01:36:04,640
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj do kraja objasnio.

2734
01:36:04,640 --> 01:36:09,859
[SPEAKER_00] Nešto najbliže onome što ja mislim da to je,

2735
01:36:09,859 --> 01:36:12,659
[SPEAKER_00] kako ga možda i društvo interpretira nekako,

2736
01:36:12,659 --> 01:36:17,979
[SPEAKER_00] da osoba shvati što želi,

2737
01:36:17,979 --> 01:36:18,840
[SPEAKER_00] tko je,

2738
01:36:18,840 --> 01:36:23,399
[SPEAKER_00] i to pokazuje bez straha

2739
01:36:23,399 --> 01:36:25,680
[SPEAKER_00] od odbacivanja zbog osude

2740
01:36:25,680 --> 01:36:27,899
[SPEAKER_00] koja dolazi izvana.

2741
01:36:27,899 --> 01:36:30,579
[SPEAKER_01] Da, jedino što...

2742
01:36:30,579 --> 01:36:32,859
[SPEAKER_00] Super bi bilo naravno kad bi našao

2743
01:36:32,859 --> 01:36:34,560
[SPEAKER_00] neki svoj krug ljudi

2744
01:36:34,560 --> 01:36:36,159
[SPEAKER_00] koji te vidi takvog, ono, ICU,

2745
01:36:36,159 --> 01:36:37,640
[SPEAKER_00] i prihvaćate takvog.

2746
01:36:37,640 --> 01:36:38,659
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam siguran da može

2747
01:36:38,659 --> 01:36:40,619
[SPEAKER_00] ljudsko običje funkcionirati

2748
01:36:40,619 --> 01:36:41,979
[SPEAKER_00] bez jedne osobe oko sebe,

2749
01:36:41,979 --> 01:36:43,340
[SPEAKER_00] ono, koja je ICU.

2750
01:36:43,340 --> 01:36:44,920
[SPEAKER_00] Bez obzira koliko si ti autentičan,

2751
01:36:44,920 --> 01:36:46,020
[SPEAKER_00] karakteran, čvrsti,

2752
01:36:46,020 --> 01:36:47,859
[SPEAKER_00] i furaš svoju furku,

2753
01:36:47,859 --> 01:36:48,720
[SPEAKER_00] kako bi se reklo.

2754
01:36:49,720 --> 01:36:51,220
[SPEAKER_00] Dosta teško.

2755
01:36:53,500 --> 01:36:55,739
[SPEAKER_01] Stoji mi sve, samo da ovaj riječ

2756
01:36:55,739 --> 01:36:57,300
[SPEAKER_01] shvatim i grebe,

2757
01:36:57,300 --> 01:37:00,100
[SPEAKER_01] jer se ne radi o svačanju,

2758
01:37:00,100 --> 01:37:01,819
[SPEAKER_01] niti se radi o trenutku,

2759
01:37:01,819 --> 01:37:03,579
[SPEAKER_01] aha, sad ja znam ko sam.

2760
01:37:03,579 --> 01:37:06,359
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, radi se o cijeloživotnom procesu.

2761
01:37:06,359 --> 01:37:08,399
[SPEAKER_01] I neko ko je autentičan,

2762
01:37:08,399 --> 01:37:09,819
[SPEAKER_01] ne zna da je autentičan,

2763
01:37:09,819 --> 01:37:11,319
[SPEAKER_01] dok se ne ukaže na to.

2764
01:37:11,319 --> 01:37:12,899
[SPEAKER_01] Neko ko nije autentičan,

2765
01:37:12,899 --> 01:37:14,420
[SPEAKER_01] samo zna da nešto ne valja,

2766
01:37:14,420 --> 01:37:16,399
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda počne svačati kroz,

2767
01:37:16,399 --> 01:37:18,500
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam, feedback ljudi ili sve.

2768
01:37:18,500 --> 01:37:20,979
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ovo nije toliko stvar svačanja.

2769
01:37:20,979 --> 01:37:22,340
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je ono,

2770
01:37:22,340 --> 01:37:24,560
[SPEAKER_01] sad ti nešto shvatiš,

2771
01:37:24,560 --> 01:37:25,920
[SPEAKER_01] pa ti bubrezi dobro rade.

2772
01:37:25,920 --> 01:37:27,979
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne, ne imaš ti veze,

2773
01:37:27,979 --> 01:37:29,479
[SPEAKER_01] te ne utičeš na svoje bubrega.

2774
01:37:29,479 --> 01:37:30,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je nešto što je

2775
01:37:30,420 --> 01:37:32,119
[SPEAKER_01] ispod nivoa svačanja.

2776
01:37:32,119 --> 01:37:33,619
[SPEAKER_01] Ali znam što si htio reći,

2777
01:37:33,619 --> 01:37:35,279
[SPEAKER_01] u smislu da spoznaš sebe,

2778
01:37:35,279 --> 01:37:36,380
[SPEAKER_01] da i onda,

2779
01:37:36,380 --> 01:37:38,340
[SPEAKER_01] ali ovdje govorimo o tome

2780
01:37:38,340 --> 01:37:39,699
[SPEAKER_01] da se ne postaje,

2781
01:37:39,699 --> 01:37:42,460
[SPEAKER_01] da može se postajati autentičan,

2782
01:37:42,460 --> 01:37:44,880
[SPEAKER_01] autentični kroz život,

2783
01:37:44,880 --> 01:37:45,899
[SPEAKER_01] kroz rad na sebi.

2784
01:37:46,939 --> 01:37:50,560
[SPEAKER_01] I isto bih htio dodati opet radi korektnosti.

2785
01:37:50,560 --> 01:37:55,760
[SPEAKER_01] Mi se možemo i tekako mijenjati kroz život,

2786
01:37:55,760 --> 01:37:59,239
[SPEAKER_01] kroz životne okolnosti, situacije,

2787
01:37:59,239 --> 01:38:01,100
[SPEAKER_01] sazrijevat.

2788
01:38:01,100 --> 01:38:03,180
[SPEAKER_01] Ono što je stvar,

2789
01:38:03,180 --> 01:38:07,420
[SPEAKER_01] samo što to nije nešto što će biti

2790
01:38:07,420 --> 01:38:09,960
[SPEAKER_01] pod musta, tako kažem.

2791
01:38:10,539 --> 01:38:12,180
[SPEAKER_01] nije izvijesno da će biti.

2792
01:38:12,180 --> 01:38:13,380
[SPEAKER_01] Postoji mogućnost

2793
01:38:13,380 --> 01:38:16,460
[SPEAKER_01] i nije sigurno da će se dešavati,

2794
01:38:16,460 --> 01:38:17,520
[SPEAKER_01] da ćemo sazrijevat.

2795
01:38:17,520 --> 01:38:20,520
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da neki rad na sebi je u stvari

2796
01:38:20,520 --> 01:38:22,699
[SPEAKER_01] aktivno bavljenje

2797
01:38:22,699 --> 01:38:25,060
[SPEAKER_01] danjim sazrijevanjem.

2798
01:38:25,060 --> 01:38:26,539
[SPEAKER_01] Što ne znači da bez tog

2799
01:38:26,539 --> 01:38:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] aktivnog bavljenja ljudi ne sazrijevaju.

2800
01:38:29,880 --> 01:38:31,840
[SPEAKER_01] Mnogi ništa nisu radili na sebi

2801
01:38:31,840 --> 01:38:33,800
[SPEAKER_01] i sazrijevaju su vrlo zdrave,

2802
01:38:33,800 --> 01:38:36,159
[SPEAKER_01] cijelovite, integrirane osobnosti.

2803
01:38:36,159 --> 01:38:38,039
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, i to treba,

2804
01:38:38,039 --> 01:38:39,859
[SPEAKER_01] jer su imali takve okolnosti,

2805
01:38:39,859 --> 01:38:41,680
[SPEAKER_01] jer su imali možda energiju,

2806
01:38:41,680 --> 01:38:43,600
[SPEAKER_01] jer su imali SQ jači.

2807
01:38:43,600 --> 01:38:46,159
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ne mora biti sve kroz rad na sebi.

2808
01:38:46,159 --> 01:38:49,439
[SPEAKER_01] Rad na sebi je konkretni nekakav rad,

2809
01:38:49,439 --> 01:38:50,760
[SPEAKER_01] dubinski što smo rekli.

2810
01:38:50,760 --> 01:38:52,939
[SPEAKER_01] Duboki rad na sebi je u biti

2811
01:38:52,939 --> 01:38:55,600
[SPEAKER_01] samo jedan strukturirani, vođeni proces,

2812
01:38:55,600 --> 01:38:59,159
[SPEAKER_01] alat koji mogu upotrijebiti,

2813
01:38:59,159 --> 01:39:03,020
[SPEAKER_01] sa idejom, ciljem da želim to i to napraviti.

2814
01:39:03,020 --> 01:39:04,739
[SPEAKER_01] I onda krenem s tim.

2815
01:39:04,739 --> 01:39:08,079
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to ne znači da nećemo sazrijevati

2816
01:39:08,079 --> 01:39:09,220
[SPEAKER_01] ovako kroz život.

2817
01:39:09,220 --> 01:39:09,859
[SPEAKER_01] Ali što kažem,

2818
01:39:09,859 --> 01:39:12,479
[SPEAKER_01] mnogi ne da ne sazrijevaju,

2819
01:39:12,479 --> 01:39:13,899
[SPEAKER_01] nego mnogi regresiraju.

2820
01:39:13,899 --> 01:39:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] I nekom od sada 65-70 godina

2821
01:39:17,000 --> 01:39:19,579
[SPEAKER_01] realno je manje godina u smislu zrelosti

2822
01:39:19,579 --> 01:39:21,939
[SPEAKER_01] nego što je možda imao prije 30 godina.

2823
01:39:21,939 --> 01:39:28,020
[SPEAKER_00] Sam bih podijelio s ovom i sa gledateljima

2824
01:39:28,020 --> 01:39:30,659
[SPEAKER_00] šta sam, do kojeg sam ja zaključka došao neki dan,

2825
01:39:30,659 --> 01:39:32,659
[SPEAKER_00] pa me zanima kratak tvoj komentar,

2826
01:39:32,659 --> 01:39:34,020
[SPEAKER_00] onda ćemo ići na zadnje pitanje.

2827
01:39:34,020 --> 01:39:38,399
[SPEAKER_00] Nekako sam ja došao do neke ideje

2828
01:39:38,399 --> 01:39:40,420
[SPEAKER_00] da je zapravo naš cilj naučiti

2829
01:39:40,420 --> 01:39:41,800
[SPEAKER_00] što više možemo,

2830
01:39:41,800 --> 01:39:43,720
[SPEAKER_00] onda to sve zaboraviti

2831
01:39:43,720 --> 01:39:44,880
[SPEAKER_00] i samo živjeti.

2832
01:39:45,619 --> 01:39:46,020
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

2833
01:39:46,020 --> 01:39:48,020
[SPEAKER_00] Ali mi se čini da bez ovog dijela,

2834
01:39:48,020 --> 01:39:50,899
[SPEAKER_00] ono da se potrudiš naučiti što više možeš u sebi,

2835
01:39:50,899 --> 01:39:52,539
[SPEAKER_00] u svijetu i tako dalje, u prirodi,

2836
01:39:52,539 --> 01:39:57,720
[SPEAKER_00] ne bi bio isti taj zadnji dio kao samo živjeti.

2837
01:39:57,720 --> 01:39:59,939
[SPEAKER_00] Znači naučiš što više možeš,

2838
01:39:59,939 --> 01:40:02,819
[SPEAKER_00] sve zaboravi i onda samo živi.

2839
01:40:03,619 --> 01:40:05,779
[SPEAKER_00] Jel ti i to sve što si naučio može biti teret?

2840
01:40:05,779 --> 01:40:11,880
[SPEAKER_01] U biti ovo otvara dodatno pitanje,

2841
01:40:11,880 --> 01:40:13,819
[SPEAKER_01] a to je šta je smisao života?

2842
01:40:13,819 --> 01:40:16,539
[SPEAKER_01] I onda imamo dva pravca.

2843
01:40:16,539 --> 01:40:19,779
[SPEAKER_01] Jedni će reći više istočna filozofija,

2844
01:40:19,779 --> 01:40:23,380
[SPEAKER_01] je smisao života je sam život.

2845
01:40:23,380 --> 01:40:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Živi život i ne filozofiraj.

2846
01:40:26,000 --> 01:40:27,300
[SPEAKER_01] Uživaj u životu.

2847
01:40:27,300 --> 01:40:28,659
[SPEAKER_00] Što nama dvojci baš ne ide?

2848
01:40:28,659 --> 01:40:32,680
[SPEAKER_01] E, zato ima drugi koncept

2849
01:40:32,680 --> 01:40:35,340
[SPEAKER_01] koji kaže, smisao života je u stvari

2850
01:40:35,340 --> 01:40:37,159
[SPEAKER_01] ispunjenje neke svoje životne svrhe.

2851
01:40:37,159 --> 01:40:40,680
[SPEAKER_01] Nečeg što ti je ono meant to be.

2852
01:40:40,680 --> 01:40:42,979
[SPEAKER_01] Nečeg što ti je dato.

2853
01:40:42,979 --> 01:40:45,939
[SPEAKER_01] Nečeg što, zašto si se rodio.

2854
01:40:45,939 --> 01:40:50,060
[SPEAKER_01] I smisao života je u stvari da pronađeš

2855
01:40:50,060 --> 01:40:51,079
[SPEAKER_01] svoju svrhu.

2856
01:40:51,079 --> 01:40:53,199
[SPEAKER_01] Koja ne mora biti da stvoriš državu

2857
01:40:53,199 --> 01:40:53,819
[SPEAKER_01] i ne znam šta.

2858
01:40:53,819 --> 01:40:57,380
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, svrhe su vrlo različite.

2859
01:40:57,380 --> 01:40:59,560
[SPEAKER_01] Bitno je ono šta tebe čini, ispunjava.

2860
01:40:59,560 --> 01:41:01,779
[SPEAKER_01] I obično je realizacija

2861
01:41:01,779 --> 01:41:04,279
[SPEAKER_01] vlastitih, originalnih

2862
01:41:04,279 --> 01:41:06,659
[SPEAKER_01] talenata, onog što nosim

2863
01:41:06,659 --> 01:41:08,159
[SPEAKER_01] u sebi, ekspresija toga

2864
01:41:08,159 --> 01:41:09,600
[SPEAKER_01] i življenje sebe

2865
01:41:09,600 --> 01:41:10,899
[SPEAKER_01] kroz ono što nosim

2866
01:41:10,899 --> 01:41:13,880
[SPEAKER_01] je u stvari ono što nosi ispunjenje.

2867
01:41:13,880 --> 01:41:15,539
[SPEAKER_01] I onda je moj život.

2868
01:41:15,539 --> 01:41:17,359
[SPEAKER_01] I onda ako to još ima nekakav

2869
01:41:17,359 --> 01:41:19,739
[SPEAKER_01] pozitivni impakt na svijet,

2870
01:41:19,739 --> 01:41:21,659
[SPEAKER_01] onda ja ispunjavam

2871
01:41:21,659 --> 01:41:22,359
[SPEAKER_01] svoju svrhu.

2872
01:41:22,859 --> 01:41:25,520
[SPEAKER_01] i onda mogu mirno otići svog svijeta jednog dana.

2873
01:41:25,520 --> 01:41:28,140
[SPEAKER_01] Osjećam se, ono, moj život je imao smisla.

2874
01:41:29,239 --> 01:41:30,500
[SPEAKER_00] Upravo je to moje zadnje pitanje.

2875
01:41:30,500 --> 01:41:33,079
[SPEAKER_00] Nekad, onako, kad

2876
01:41:33,079 --> 01:41:35,479
[SPEAKER_00] filozofiram sam sa sobom

2877
01:41:35,479 --> 01:41:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] pa mi mašta

2878
01:41:37,000 --> 01:41:38,859
[SPEAKER_00] radi s to na sad,

2879
01:41:38,859 --> 01:41:41,640
[SPEAKER_00] razmišljam o smrti.

2880
01:41:43,359 --> 01:41:45,720
[SPEAKER_00] I nedavno sam imao misao

2881
